flowchart TB
    N1["1. Entry domain: L2 batch | previous state root | execution parameters"]
    N2["2. Normalization: shape external inputs into a verifiable domain model"]
    N3["3. Core mechanism: Validate batch shape | Apply deterministic transition | Commit new state root"]
    N4["4. State and commitment: input digest, transition digest, and output digest"]
    N5["5. Evidence or result: execution trace | new state root | public proof inputs"]
    N6["6. Consumer boundary: neo-zkvm-guest | neo-zkvm-host | gateway services"]
    N7["7. Failure path: input violates constraints or output cannot be verified"]
    N8["8. Extension point: input adapters, output adapters, and monitoring surfaces"]
    N1 --> N2
    N1 --> N3
    N1 --> N4
    N1 --> N5
    N1 --> N6
    N1 --> N7
    N1 --> N8
    N2 -. constrains .-> N4
    N4 -. produces .-> N5
    N5 -. consumed by .-> N6
    classDef core fill:#0f172a,stroke:#38bdf8,color:#e5f2ff,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef support fill:#111827,stroke:#64748b,color:#f8fafc;
    class N1 core;
    class N2,N3,N4,N5,N6,N7,N8 support;
